works.description: For those who love pimped rides, Cooper Tires has created a very unique set of diamond-encrusted tires to commemorate 60 years of British Formula 3 racing. London jewelers, FK Diamonds has designed the bejeweled tires through a meticulous process of setting each jewel to the tires on a Cooper logo cutout in metal. The setting features a mixture of diamonds and Swarovski crystals. Below is a video by the company showing the tires in the making. The specially designed tires were shown off at the Silverstone launch of the 2011 Cooper Tire British F3 International Series
